  "slug": "health-indicator-player",
  "title": "Player Health Indicator",
  "description": "See Opponents health bar / hearts  easily",
  "body": "<p>This texture pack displays the health of any player, but it calculates it based on <strong>percentage rather than actual health values</strong>. Because of this, the hearts shown may not match the player&rsquo;s real health in certain situations.</p>\n\n<p>In normal gameplay with default health values, this usually isn&rsquo;t noticeable, and the display will appear accurate. However, in modded or custom scenarios with increased health, the difference becomes clear.</p>\n<h2>How to Use</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and install the texture pack</li>\n<li>Install&nbsp;<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/use/installer/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Fabric</a></li>\n<li>Ensure you have&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entity-model-features\">EMF</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entitytexturefeatures\">ETF</a>&nbsp;in your mods folder</li>\n<li>Launch your game and activate</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_624405e9-664e-456b-89c8-25ceeb8156e3.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>",
